description:
Rory is a personal trainer who bears a striking resemblance to Vin Diesel.

The thing I noticed immediately about Rory is that he is confident... very confident.

“You don’t hold anything back do you?”

He laughed. “No, I’ve never been that way. I’m definitely not shy.”

He was excited about showing us some of his moves.

“I love jumping, anything that involves explosive movements,” he explained. “It’s the best way to get in shape.”
title: Rory
